          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">μηρίον</span></b> : only pl., <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">μηρία</span> and <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">μῆρα</span>, pieces of meat from the thighs (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">μηροί</span>) of victims, <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">thigh -
